verses.verse: To the chief <S%H5329>Musician,<s%> A Psalm of <S%H1732>David.<s%> The <S%H5036>fool<s%> hath <S%H559>said<s%> in his <S%H3820>heart,<s%> There is <S%H369>no<s%> <S%H430>God.<s%> They are <S%H7843>corrupt,<s%> they have done <S%H8581>abominable<s%> <S%H5949>works,<s%> there is <S%H369>none<s%> that <S%H6213>doeth<s%> <S%H2896>good.<s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> looked <S%H8259>down<s%> from <S%H4480>heaven<s%> <S%H8064><s%> <S%H5921>upon<s%> the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H120>men,<s%> to <S%H7200>see<s%> if there <S%H3426>were<s%> any that did <S%H7919>understand,<s%> and <S%H1875>seek<s%> <S%H853><s%> <S%H430>God.<s%>

They are <S%H3605>all<s%> gone <S%H5493>aside,<s%> they are all <S%H3162>together<s%> become <S%H444>filthy:<s%> there is <S%H369>none<s%> that <S%H6213>doeth<s%> <S%H2896>good,<s%> <S%H369>no,<s%> <S%H1571>not<s%> <S%H259>one.<s%>

Have <S%H3605>all<s%> the <S%H6466>workers<s%> of <S%H205>iniquity<s%> <S%H3808>no<s%> <S%H3045>knowledge?<s%> who eat <S%H398>up<s%> my <S%H5971>people<s%> as they <S%H398>eat<s%> <S%H3899>bread,<s%> and <S%H7121>call<s%> <S%H3808>not<s%> upon the <S%H3068>LORD.<s%>
There <S%H8033><s%> were they in great <S%H6342>fear:<s%> <S%H6343><s%> <S%H3588>for<s%> <S%H430>God<s%> is in the <S%H1755>generation<s%> of the <S%H6662>righteous.<s%>
Ye have <S%H954>shamed<s%> the <S%H6098>counsel<s%> of the <S%H6041>poor,<s%> <S%H3588>because<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> is his <S%H4268>refuge.<s%>

Oh <S%H4310>that<s%> <S%H5414><s%> the <S%H3444>salvation<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> were come out of <S%H4480>Zion!<s%> <S%H6726><s%> when the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> bringeth <S%H7725>back<s%> the <S%H7622>captivity<s%> of his <S%H5971>people,<s%> <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> shall <S%H1523>rejoice,<s%> and <S%H3478>Israel<s%> shall be <S%H8055>glad.<s%>
